Field constraints:
- `name`: lowercase kebab-case, product-quality name (not paper-title-as-slug)
- `problem`: plain English, focused on the buyer's pain point
- `source_url`: must be an arXiv URL from the papers above
- `solution`: reference the paper's technique, explain the product form factor
- `language`: one of: go, python, typescript, bash, rust. Pick the best fit for the tool type (Go for CLI/infra, Python for ML tooling, TypeScript for MCP servers)
- `files`: list of file paths — include test files
- `estimated_lines`: integer, 100-300

